quran[9{c,v,t}:
10,34,"inn se pucho, tumahray tehra-ay hue sharikon mein koi hai jo takhleeq ki ibtida bhi karta ho aur phir is ka iada bhi kere? kaho woh sirf Allah hai jo takhleeq ki ibtida bhi karta hai aur is ka iada bhi, phir tum yeh kis Ulti raah par chalaye ja rahay ho ?"
10,35,"inn se pucho tumahray tehra-ay hue sharikon mein koi aisa bhi hai jo haq ki taraf rahnumai karta ho? kaho woh sirf Allah hai jo haq ki taraf rahnumai karta hai phir bhala batao, jo haq ki taraf rahnumai karta hai woh iss ka ziyada mustahiq hai ke is ki pairwi ki jaye ya woh jo khud raah nahi paata ila yeh ke is ki rahnumai ki jaye? aakhir tumhe ho kya gaya hai, kaisay ultay ultay faislay karte ho ?"
10,36,"haqeeqat yeh hai ke inn mein se aksar log mehez qiyaas o gumaan ke peechay chalay ja rahay hain, halan ke gumaan haq ki zaroorat ko kuch bhi poora nahi karta jo kuch yeh kar rahay hain Allah uss ko khoob jaanta hai"
10,37,aur yeh quran woh cheez nahi hai jo Allah ki wahi o taleem ke baghair tasneef kar liya jaye balkay yeh to jo kuch pehlay aa chuka tha is ki tasdeeq aur al-kitab ki tafseel hai iss mein koi shak nahi ke yeh frmanrwaye kaayenaat ki taraf se hai
10,38,"kya yeh log kehte hain kePeghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallamne usay khud tasneef kar liya hai? kaho, “ agar tum apne is ilzaam mein sachey ho to aik soorah is jaisi tasneef kar lao aur aik khuda ko chore kar jis jis ko bُla satke ho madad ke liye bُla lau """
10,39,"asal yeh hai ke jo cheez inn ke ilm ki girift mein nahi aayi aur jis ka مآل bhi un ke samnay nahi aaya, uss ko unhon ne ( khamkhuwa atkal pacho ) jhutla diya isi terhan to un se pehlay ke log bhi jhutla chuke hain phir dekh lau unn zaalmon ka kya injaam howa"
10,40,inn mein se kuch log imaan layein ge aur kuch nahi layein ge aur tera rab unn mfsdon ko khoob jaanta hai
10,41,"agar yeh tujhe jutlatay hain to keh day ke “mera amal mere liye hai aur tumhara amal tumahray liye, jo kuch mein karta hon is ki zimma daari se tum bari ho aur jo kuch tum kar rahay ho is ki zimma daari se mein bari hon """
10,42,"un mein bohat se log hain jo teri baatein suntay hain, magar kya to behroon ko sunayega khuwa woh kuch nah samajte hon ?"
